name: EN EXPAND ALL-S GR
summary: This index is the EN Expand All-S GR index. It tracks the performance of a broad range of companies listed on the Oslo Stock Exchange, with a focus on sustainability, and is a gross return index. The index is designed for investors seeking broad exposure to the Norwegian market with a sustainability focus.

name: OBX BASIC MAT GR
summary: This index is the OBX Basic Materials GR index. It tracks the performance of companies in the OBX index that are classified within the basic materials sector and is a gross return index. The index serves as a benchmark for investors interested in tracking the performance of basic material companies within the Norwegian market.
